  "text": "Single-genome/proviral sequencing We performed single-genome/proviral sequencing of HIV-1 env (V1-V3) as previously described for all six participants [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . For participants 5, 6, and 7, we also sequenced a 2.1-kb region from p24 to reverse transcriptase [CITATION_3] . See Supplemental Digital Content 1 (http://links.lww.com/QAD/B40) for primers and PCR conditions. Single HIV-1 molecules were sequenced using Sanger sequencing (Australian Genome Research Facility, Sydney, Australia).",
